{"tid":1052703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[THUG LIFE]屯門醫院急症科副顧問醫生　涉當值吸大麻被捕","createTime":"2019-03-08T13:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T15:01:13.000Z","uid":75610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"efc1d170543c1527bd508220b8f8ac6b4a0b6f10","tid":1052703,"uid":75610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T13:15:31.000Z","msg":"消息指出，屯門醫院急症科一名甄姓副顧問醫生當值期間涉嫌吸食大麻，據悉其年資不淺。屯門醫院發言人證實，周二（5日）晚上11時許，該院急症科一名醫生當值期間一度離開工作崗位，同事透過廣播及手提電話尋找不果。該醫生於午夜時分返回工作間，同事發現其精神及情緒有異樣。院方已暫停有關醫生臨牀職務。警方表示，已拘捕涉案男子。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屯門醫院續稱，已安排該院急症科部門主管及資深醫生，檢視該醫生本月份當值期間的診症紀錄，確定所有病人均得到適當治療；為確保沒有其他病人受影響，有關部門亦正檢視該醫生過去三個月處理過的個案。<br />\n<br />\n屯門醫院表示，對事件非常重視，會嚴肅跟進員工不當行為，並已就事件報警。<br />\n<br />\n警方今日下午接獲一相關機構職員報案，指其機構一名男醫護人員懷疑早前曾吸食毒品。警方經初步調查後，今日在田心區拘捕該名48歲姓甄男子，涉嫌「吸食毒品」。<br />\n<br />\n被捕男子現正被扣留調查。案件由屯門警區重案組跟進調查。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190308/s00001/1552043832948/%e5%b1%af%e9%96%80%e9%86%ab%e9%99%a2%e6%80%a5%e7%97%87%e7%a7%91%e5%89%af%e9%a1%a7%e5%95%8f%e9%86%ab%e7%94%9f-%e6%b6%89%e7%95%b6%e5%80%bc%e5%90%b8%e5%a4%a7%e9%ba%bb%e8%a2%ab%e6%8d%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190308%2Fs00001%2F1552043832948%2F%25e5%25b1%25af%25e9%2596%2580%25e9%2586%25ab%25e9%2599%25a2%25e6%2580%25a5%25e7%2597%2587%25e7%25a7%2591%25e5%2589%25af%25e9%25a1%25a7%25e5%2595%258f%25e9%2586%25ab%25e7%2594%259f-%25e6%25b6%2589%25e7%2595%25b6%25e5%2580%25bc%25e5%2590%25b8%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e9%25ba%25bb%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%258d%2595&d=fEJCtfATBeMWJ6YDVJZPMgogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=90b28c96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190308%2Fs00001%2F1552043832948%2F%25e5%25b1%25af%25e9%2596%2580%25e9%2586%25ab%25e9%2599%25a2%25e6%2580%25a5%25e7%2597%2587%25e7%25a7%2591%25e5%2589%25af%25e9%25a1%25a7%25e5%2595%258f%25e9%2586%25ab%25e7%2594%259f-%25e6%25b6%2589%25e7%2595%25b6%25e5%2580%25bc%25e5%2590%25b8%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e9%25ba%25bb%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%258d%2595&h=21677bfa\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190308/s00001/1552043832948/%e5%b1%af%e9%96%80%e9%86%ab%e9%99%a2%e6%80%a5%e7%97%87%e7%a7%91%e5%89%af%e9%a1%a7%e5%95%8f%e9%86%ab%e7%94%9f-%e6%b6%89%e7%95%b6%e5%80%bc%e5%90%b8%e5%a4%a7%e9%ba%bb%e8%a2%ab%e6%8d%95</a>"},{"pid":"b2191472cc1720633ffe53ee0b82df6afe1d170e","tid":1052703,"uid":207101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T13:17:11.000Z","msg":"食燒賣魚蛋食厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f74edd1e06929c8ea580ac99e61745f3e474060","tid":1052703,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T14:52:37.000Z","msg":"仲話食大麻好過食煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a29226be8c73f08c1adad678b7ecaf8731cff3fe","tid":1052703,"uid":46013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T15:01:13.000Z","msg":"連醫生都係道友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}